    "7110307": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Little Mao",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "#Look, {NICKNAME}, look! It's a scene of ancient people attending a festival and performing a ritual. Pretty different from the festivals we have today, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Although the grown-ups in the city and the village all say that the Lord of Geo was the first to arrive in Chenyu Vale, I've heard that the people in the picture actually got here even earlier than he did!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "People back then used to throw bits of magic jade into the river, and they'd float along until they sank to the bottom. They saw it as a way to guarantee good weather, prevent the river from flooding, and ensure that the soil would be fertile."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Based on what we previously discussed, I'm guessing that Chenyu Vale will only be fixed after we've found some jade that was thrown into the river in ancient times! That makes sense, doesn't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow, you're so knowledgeable! Was your friend also the one who told you these stories?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You rule, Little Mao! That's first-class guide material right there!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmph! Little Mao's a local, so of course he understands this place better than Paimon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "These legends are fascinating."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Yep, and... Everyone'll be really blessed and live happily ever after, and all that..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Hehe, but I much prefer hearing her stories about ancient wars and battles... She told me that the warriors back then were all giants who were over ten feet tall!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "The warriors of Chenyu Vale were covered in tattoos, and they had these massive jade axes that could chop a person in half in the blink of an eye!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "And the Millelith, led by none other than the Lord of Geo himself, were even tougher! They clad themselves in suits of armor that weighed over a thousand pounds and fought with hundred-pound spears! Apparently, everyone was at war back then, so much so that Bishui River turned crimson red..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Later on, the mountains to the south became full of ghosts from that era. Even now, those who wander through the mountains might still be able to catch their singing on the wind..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ergh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yikes, scary stuff! Cover your ears, Mini Pie."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmph, who's Mini Pie? Hautemontagne's right though — if you constantly think about this stuff, you'll turn into a villain when you're older!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't think these stories are meant for kids..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah... It sounds terrifying! Hautemontagne's right, you shouldn't dwell on this stuff all the time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Hehe... There's no way grown-ups would tell us these stories. They always say we're too young to hear them, that they'll turn us rotten, and stuff like that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "But I'm old enough already! Hearing a story's not going to turn me into a monster. Besides, there aren't many adults still around who know these stories anyway. If my friend hadn't told me, I wouldn't even have known the stories about this picture!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Okay, fine then, guess we'll move on."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "So... the grown-ups were right to say that those ancient people threw the jade into the river from somewhere high up... but where exactly? And where did all the jade float off to...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh... Well, it must have sunk to the bottom, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "It's not that simple... If it was thrown in somewhere upriver, and even if it sank to the bottom, it would still be pushed downriver by the current. Let alone after so many years..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Besides, I've never heard talk of any ancient ritual jade being found upriver... Chenyu Vale is a small place, after all. If there had been such rumors, everyone would already know about them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hehe, you know so much. You're future scholar material for sure!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Hehe... But what if I don't want to be a scholar? They don't earn much Mora, and it sounds like no fun!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Then become a traveler, just like us! What could be more fun than adventuring around the world?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Hmm... Seeing as we now know the site of the Rainjade Rite, what should we do next?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why don't we go somewhere high up to take a look?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "High up, hmm... The watchtower at Yilong Wharf's pretty high up!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's observe how the river flows."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "If we want to see how the river flows..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Maybe it would be a good idea to try the tall watchtower over at Yilong Wharf?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Hehe, you're a clever one, Ms. Paimon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hehe, of course!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Okay, let's head out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Alright! Let's go!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I want to take another look around."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Okay! Let me know when you're ready."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
