    "7110339": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Little Mao",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh. Seems like the jade's starting to move..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "That's right. But according to the story, the riverbed should have lots of other Votive Rainjades. Why does Big Sis Fujin only want this one?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Look! It's shining, almost as if it's resonating with the adeptal energy on you, {NICKNAME}!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Why don't we try using that power, eh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "That should do it. Wow, awesome! It suddenly became small!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah! Paimon didn't think it'd just change size like that. Guess that's a millennia-old treasure for you... It's just like you said, Little Mao! \"They could be as tall as the clouds, or small enough to hide amidst pool and leaf...\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "#Yeah! Well, looks like the Votive Rainjade's in our hands now. You're so reliable, {NICKNAME}!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, Paimon worked hard too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Ms. Paimon's amazing! So you're going to take us to that \"deep pool shrouded in cloud and mist to the south\" now, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Clouds and mist... Hmm... I think Chenyu Vale really does have places like that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But where? Tell us, little guide, and Paimon'll take you there!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Do you remember the place Mountain mentioned, the spot where we met? That place is super foggy, and I know of a secret cavern that leads there. Even the other locals don't know about it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "It was my friend who showed me the way, and since you're my friend too, Paimon, I'll tell you all about it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You've got an amazing friend, Little Mao."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Hehe, of course. Uh, well, you're both pretty impressive too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Your friend in the mountains... Are they connected to Adeptus Fujin?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "...She's told me lots of stories, and quite a few of them were about Big Sis Fujin."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, any friend of yours is a friend of ours too! In fact, Paimon hopes we'll meet her on the way."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Shall we go? Paimon's gonna take you all to the... place you mentioned, Little Mao!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Take us away, Ms. Paimon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alrighty then. Let's go!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Give me a moment. Let's see if there are any treasure chests that we haven't found yet..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Seriously? There's no helping you, huh? Hang on a moment, alright, Little Mao?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Okay! The cavern's pretty dark, so you've gotta be careful!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
