    "7110067": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Fujin",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The Sacred Simulacra are all ready!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Thank you both. The Votive Rainjade has been returned to its priests, and the statues have come back to their rightful places. The Rainjade Rite is now ready to be performed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "...But will Chenyu Vale really recover once you cast the Rainjade in?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "That's right. Things will get better for us, Little Mao. Nature, jade, humans... All is divinely dictated. The changes in the land and water in Chenyu Vale, the malicious fog in the spirit veins... They are all essentially a sign of the earth moving against the flow of time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah. Huh, so that miasma-like thing is a manifestation of environmental disorder...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Hehe, that's right. You can think of it like Chenyu Vale's attempt to... How to put it? Return to nature? And what we intend to do here is to treat the land and soil, and rid it of this sickness."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "\"Return to nature\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "After all, before humans left their caves and mountains to dominate the world and regulate nature, and before Chenyu Vale or Bishui River got those names, the land, mountains, and rivers had their own order."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Hehe, even I sometimes miss the cool mountain streams, and the great rivers that would ebb and flow with the seasons. I mean, I was once a mere fish that swam..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "But if we let nature seize control of its order once more, the people of Chenyu Vale will suffer and languish. I hope you can understand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Yeah..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "In that case..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Did it work?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That thing in the fog just now..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Nothing seems to have changed..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "It seems I am too feeble in my current state."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh? We got the Votive Rainjade, and we placed the Simulacra, but it still wasn't enough?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "I'm very sorry — it is not your fault. I need more power to overcome this trial. Just as the adeptal energy in the Votive Rainjade has dissipated into the spirit veins, so has my power also left me across the long years."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Huh? Will you grow really big just like the jade?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "P—Probably not...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hehe, just think about it, though — Super Adeptus Fujin, now three times the size! Well, is there any way we can restore your power?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Golden Carp."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "#Ah, {NICKNAME}, you are wise indeed. Before you found a few Golden Carp, I could not even muster the strength to appear. Initially, I thought that we just needed to gather all the ritual implements, and that would make up for the deficiency in my power..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "...I was not entirely open with you before, but neither the present nor past me was anywhere near a match for the adepti of the south. I... feared you would consider me weak and unworthy of your help..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Gee, is that it? Paimon thought you'd have something more important to say!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Eh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "There's no way we'd abandon or not make friends with you just because of that!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "#That I, the {M#Young Master}{F#Young Lady}, consider you a friend is not conditional on your status as an adeptus."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Other than that whole \"{M#Young Master}{F#Young Lady}\" bit, Paimon wanted to say the same thing!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That you are my friend has nothing to do with your status as an adeptus."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "My friend told me lots of stories about you. In my mind, even though we've just met, we're already friends, and I also want you to be happy, Big Sis!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Alright, alright... Thank you, all of you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, that's more like it! So, where should we start looking for these Golden Carp?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "I believe that you will have to go to Yaodie Valley. There will be a cavern there with a Golden Carp hidden within."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
