    "7110068": {
        "Desc": "Check the clues nearby",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "We're here, Big Sis Fujin! Have you been waiting for us here all this time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "#Hehe, no, no. After leaving Carp's Rest, I can only appear in places in which my power remains, and only by the grace of your adeptal energy, {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait a minute... Didn't the gap in the middle of that mural originally have something that went with the Golden Carp mural in it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "...I'm not sure. In truth, this is my first time seeing this mural as well."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "I'm sure you've all heard of the battles that took place in the past."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Khaenri'ah..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Hmm?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Sorry, I am merely a minor adeptus of Chenyu Vale. I fear I know little about any wars concerning this \"Khaenri'ah.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The Archon War?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Archon War..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Yes. This cave was one of the shelters we built for the inhabitants of Chenyu Vale, such that the innocents caught in the crossfire when the floods overturned the heavens and the earth split open could have a place of safety."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "I didn't expect that they'd draw a mural here, though. I believe the ones depicted to be me... *cough* I mean, the \"big, slippery Carp\" Little Mao mentioned, and a friend."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Huh... If that's the case, why did the most important part get taken somewhere else?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "That's true. Why is that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "...Perhaps dissatisfaction. The three of us were once great friends, with two of us becoming worshipped as adepti, and one of us was always the mountain's master."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Later, Herblord and I defected together, and she most likely died too. Or perhaps, the one amongst us who fought to the last never submitted, and only heard news of us afterward."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Perhaps, to her, we were all traitors, with the depictions of myself and Herblord becoming an object for her to vent her fury against."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Little Mao",
                    "T": "Huh... Is that really the case? The painting outside looks like..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Who knows? In any case, that's all in the past."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "So please, lend me your strength in nursing Chenyu Vale back to health. I can feel that there's another Golden Carp lingering where I used to... Near Mt. Xuanlian, I believe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Oh, so there's another?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "If we get that one, I should have enough strength to perform the ritual."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "Speaking of that, I must apologize for being unable to control the Golden Carp even with you nearby. I know they might have given you some trouble, swimming through the air like that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That was somewhat troublesome, yes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's fine, I just think of them like Seelies."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But really, where is the Golden Carp that should be here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fujin",
                    "T": "#Hehe, well, inside the painting. Just use your adeptal energy to awaken it, {NICKNAME}."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
